    <li><a href="/docs/configuration/accessories">Set up database and cache accessories</a></li>
    <li><a href="/docs/features/secrets">Learn more about secrets management</a></li>
    <li><a href="/docs/ci/github">Set up GitHub Actions CI/CD</a></li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
